{{Infobox dungeon |name = Glittering Cave |image = [[File:Glittering Cave.png|150px]] |caption = A map of Glittering Cave. |tokens = 505,000 |location = West of Route 9 }} '''Glittering Cave''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kalos]]. It initially has 100 tiles arranged in a 10x10 square, including 10 chest tiles, 23 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
